          <ul>
            <li><strong>3 copies</strong> of important data</li>
            <li><strong>2 different storage types</strong> (e.g., local drive and cloud)</li>
            <li><strong>1 copy offsite</strong> (cloud storage or backup drive kept elsewhere)</li>
          </ul>

